#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.1.3.rst:4
msgid ""
"pytest-2.1.3 is a minor backward compatible maintenance release of the "
"popular py.test testing tool.  It is commonly used for unit, functional- and "
"integration testing.  See extensive docs with examples here:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.1.3.rst:8
msgid "http://pytest.org/"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.1.3.rst:10
msgid ""
"The release contains another fix to the perfected assertions introduced with "
"the 2.1 series as well as the new possibility to customize reporting for "
"assertion expressions on a per-directory level."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.1.3.rst:14
msgid "If you want to install or upgrade pytest, just type one of::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/announce/release-2.1.3.rst:16
msgid ""
"pip install -U pytest # or\n"
"easy_install -U pytest"
msgstr ""

